body:
Since Lux will soon become very popular, I would like to look into what champions to pick against her
http://i.imgur.com/9PBcVQQ.jpg

A: is a water type. Use electric type and grass type pokemon when facing her while avoiding fire types. 
Good choices: {{champion:85}}  {{champion:143}}  Bad Choices:{{champion:1}} {{champion:63}} 

B: A grass type. Unlike A, fire and ice types as well as poison types are really good against her but water types and rock types are a big nono.
Good: {{champion:69}} {{champion:34}} Bad: {{champion:54}} {{champion:267}} 

C: Flying type: Use electric and rock types versus this form while avoiding fighting and grass types
Good: {{champion:85}} {{champion:163}}  Bad: {{champion:64}} {{champion:57}} 

D: Fire type. Fire types are weak to ground and rock type champions while strong against ice, bug and steel
Good: {{champion:33}} {{champion:268}}  Bad: {{champion:121}} {{champion:82}}

E: A Dark type. Use Fairy type and fighting type attacks. Avoid Psychic types as they have no affect on her. Also has good resistance vs dark types
Good: {{champion:2}} {{champion:117}}  Bad:{{champion:238}}  {{champion:56}} 

F: Psychic Type. Ghost types are super effective along with dark types. Don&#039;t use fighting types or poison.
Good: {{champion:30}} {{champion:429}} Bad: {{champion:27}}  {{champion:59}} 

G: Seems like a dual type of rock/fire. Best types are water and ground. Avoid using fire and normal types as you only deal 1/4 and 1/2 damage respectavely.
Good: {{champion:72}} {{champion:223}}  Bad: {{champion:119}} {{champion:115}} 

H: Electric Type. This one is tough as her only weakness is ground type.  Flying types are not advised when fighting her.
Good: {{champion:421}} {{champion:3}} Bad: {{champion:133}} {{champion:161}} 

I: Fairy Type. Use poison and steel types. avoid dragon types as they deal no damage to her
Good: {{champion:17}} {{champion:53}} Bad: {{champion:136}} {{champion:102}} 

J: Finally the ice type. Best choice would be Fire and Fighting. Grass and Flying will have trouble though
Good: {{champion:10}} {{champion:89}} Bad: {{champion:40}} {{champion:266}} 

Final Note: Riot has nnot announced it but it may seem like almost all of the Lux&#039;s forms will be dual types with psychic as their 2nd type. In which case I would look at F for what to use.
